4. What to look at next\n\nLet me search more specifically. The user mentioned \"Ennin\" with an 'i' not \"Enning\" with an 'e' - so I should look for the correct spelling. Let me also check if there are files about Deborah outside the Downloads folder (since the user said \"all that ive done for her so far\" which might be elsewhere).\n\nI need to focus the search since the Downloads folder has tens of thousands of files. Let me narrow down to:\n- Just the chat log files\n- The specific Deborah-related PDFs\n- Any documents or notes about her health\n\nLet me run more focused searches in parallel.",
