      "text": "---\n## Goal\n- Audit all files in `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads` related to **Deborah Efua Ennin's diabetes**, plus all work Andie has done for her so far, where things stand, and what to look at next.\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n- PowerShell only on Windows; no recursive drive scans; max 2 retries on a failed approach.\n- User said \"carry on\" — continue gathering context before reporting.\n- Output a clear, prioritized summary of files, current state, and next actions.\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n- Pulled first 300 lines + last 336 lines of `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\_chat 12 (2).txt` (WhatsApp with Mum, span 31/01/2023 → 03/06/2026).\n- Read 4 AI chat logs in `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\PIP Re-application\\`: `Completing PIP Review Submission.md`, `Great_Completing PIP Review Submission.md`, `PIP&Laura.md`, `Securing Emergency Training Funding.md`.\n- Identified the December 2025 health intervention: `Deborah_Plain_Language_Record.docx` (15-page NHS plain-language guide) — converted to text via Python; content confirmed.\n- Read `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\GHPassDeborah_merged (1).pdf` (7 pages, May 2026) — Ghana High Commission visa application pack for Deborah.\n- Confirmed active workstream: **PIP re-application** under `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\PIP Re-application\\`.\n\n### In Progress\n- Building the consolidated picture of: files / work done / current status / next steps for the user.\n\n### Blocked\n- `C:\\Users\\LLM-Test\\Downloads\\Deborah_s_Health_Crossroads.pdf` — Read tool returned **\"File not found\"** even though the file is listed; path likely has hidden chars or a different actual filename (suspect it is the PDF export of `Deborah_Plain_Language_Record.docx`, content matches).\n- `.NET DocumentFormat.OpenXml` assembly not present; used Python `zipfile`+regex fallback successfully for the docx.\n- Recursive scan of full `Downloads` folder times out at 180s — must scope by name/keyword filters only.\n\n#